Voyager New Moves

Oxidize

Type Category PP Power Accuracy Description
5 0 Restores HP. The amount varies with the weather.

Details

This new move restores inverts the weather behavior of Synthesis.

This move restores 1/2 the user's maximum HP in no weather; 2/3 in heavy rain or a thunderstorm; and 1/4 in any other weather event.
